Installing software packages:

Docker-engine:

1. Check updates for " apt ", by the command apt get updates
2. Install docker engine by the command apt install docker.io
3. Installing services as images from docker hub
   docker pull "image-name"
   docker images( shows installed images)
   docker run -itd "image-name" (create container for particular image)
   docker ps (check running  container)
   docker start/stop "conatiner-id" (start/stop contaier)
   docker run -itd "image-name" /bin/bash (login into container)
   
Docker-compose:
 
 Install docker-compose by the command apt install docker-compose

Git:

 Install git (apt install git)

